{"tiddlers": {
"$:/plugins/dyp/Sidenote & Sidelink/macros/macro": {
    "created": "20240131061413701",
    "text": "\define sidenote(title, content)
<span class="sidenote-number"></span>
<div class="yin">*显示批注
<div class="sidenote">
<details>
<summary>$title$</summary>
<blockquote>
<span class="break">
$content$
</span>
</blockquote>
</details>
</div>
<div>
\end

\define sidelink(link, title)
<span class="sidenote-number"></span>
<div class="yin"><$link to=$link$ tooltip="跳转到引用条目">*$title$</$link>
<div class="sidenote">
<details>
<summary>$title$</summary>
<blockquote>
<span class="break">
<$transclude tiddler=$link$>
</span>
</blockquote>
</details>
</div>
<div>
\end",
    "title": "$:/plugins/dyp/Sidenote & Sidelink/macros/macro",
    "type": "text/vnd.tiddlywiki",
    "tags": "$:/tags/Macro",
    "modified": "20240131061855081"
},

"$:/plugins/dyp/Sidenote & Sidelink/readme": {
    "created": "20240131061054438",
    "text": "; Sidenote & Sidelink: 条目侧边批注
"""
用法：

`<<sidenote "小标题" "内容">>` （小标题和内容都可以重复，内容可以换行）
`<<sidelink "条目标题" "小标题">>` （链接到的条目标题不可重复，小标题可重复）
"""",
    "title": "$:/plugins/dyp/Sidenote & Sidelink/readme",
    "type": "text/vnd.tiddlywiki",
    "tags": "",
    "modified": "20240131062225957"
